Name: Nausea
Description: Nausea allows your disease to spread through mouth to mouth contact and draws some attention to it.

Name: Rash
Description: People avoid the infected more but they are more contagious. And more visible.

Name: Indigestion
Description: Problems in the digestive tract can be uncomfortable and negatively imact quality of life.

Name: Fatigue
Description: Fatigue weakens the immune system of the infected.

Name: Vomiting
Description: Vomiting brings a lot of attention but also can make the infected frail and weak.

Name: Anemia
Description: Can lead to feelings of weakness and low blood levels.

Name: Fever
Description: Fevers can be deadly.

Name: Diarrhea
Description: Diarrhea and its dehydrating effects can be deadly and can spread infection to the water supply.

Name: Hives
Description: Painful stinging rash that itches badly.

Name: Eczema
Description: Red and inflammed skin that is itchy and dry.

Name: Stomach Ulcer
Description: Extremely painful hole in your stomach.

Name: Depression
Description: Weakens your immune system. Makes you sad.

Name: Anxiety
Description: The fear and worry can make you tense and tired and too weak to fight infection.

Name: Heart Pain
Description: This is discomforting and dangerous and a sign of worse symptoms to come.

Name: Weight Gain
Description: Comes from the parasite taking all essential nutrients and only leaving fats and sugars for you. Very dangerous.

Name: Tachycardia
Description: Dangerous heart condition where the heart beats too fast. Can be deadly depending on speed and severity.

Name: Heart Attack
Description: Heart attacks are very likely to be fatal.

Name: Hemorrhoids
Description: Extremely painful anal structures which cause swelling and discomfort.

Name: Insomnia
Description: Insomnia weakens immune system responses.

Name: Inflammation
Description: Inflammation is harmful and disrupting for many bodily processes. Can be deadly

Name: Paralysis
Description: Paralysis is deadly but makes it much less likely for infected to infect others.

Name: Coma
Description: Comas are very deadly and make it much less likely for infected to infect others.

Name: Delirium
Description: Delerium comes after not sleeping for way too long. It is very dangerous and very noticeable.

Name: Heat Resistance III

Name: Cold Resistance III

Name: Wet Resistance III

Name: Medicinal Resistance II

Name: Medicinal Resistance III

Name: Water Transmission II

Name: Water Transmission III
